rocessed linear data as picture and used GAN to recover the heating event with only hundreds of well-chosen pictures</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Heavy Ion Research","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"tracedSVG":"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='400'%20height='210'%20viewBox='0%200%20400%20210'%20preserveAspectRatio='none'%3e%3cpath%20d='M75%2092v2h89v-5H75v3'%20fill='%2364ffda'%20fill-rule='evenodd'/%3e%3c/svg%3e","aspectRatio":1.9021739130434783,"src":"/static/72d7b7b319f31e7558ba33ba57bed5cd/73c85/heavy.png","srcSet":"/static/72d7b7b319f31e7558ba33ba57bed5cd/d4144/heavy.png 175w,\n/static/72d7b7b319f31e7558ba33ba57bed5cd/a5370/heavy.png 350w,\n/static/72d7b7b319f31e7558ba33ba57bed5cd/73c85/heavy.png 700w,\n/static/72d7b7b319f31e7558ba33ba57bed5cd/4ff95/heavy.png 1050w,\n/static/72d7b7b319f31e7558ba33ba57bed5cd/7cdbc/heavy.png 1116w","srcWebp":"/static/72d7b7b319f31e7558ba33ba57bed5cd/47203/heavy.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/72d7b7b319f31e7558ba33ba57bed5cd/5575a/heavy.webp 175w,\n/static/72d7b7b319f31e7558ba33ba57bed5cd/8ea22/heavy.webp 350w,\n/static/72d7b7b319f31e7558ba33ba57bed5cd/47203/heavy.webp 700w,\n/static/72d7b7b319f31e7558ba33ba57bed5cd/565e9/heavy.webp 1050w,\n/static/72d7b7b319f31e7558ba33ba57bed5cd/2cc04/heavy.webp 1116w","sizes":"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px"}}},"tech":["ROOT","TMVA","C++"],"github":"","external":"https://zxqlxy.synology.me:5001/d/f/438834080071553799"},"html":"<p>Analyzed the data of tens of millions of collisions of J/psi mesons and strange charm mesons collected from <a href=\"https://home.cern/science/accelerators/large-hadron-collider\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">LHC</a>. Used boost decision tree, rectangular cut and MLP to train the data to get a better selection of the signal through <a href=\"http://tmva.sourceforge.net/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">TMVA</a>. Manipulated data stored in trees and visualized them via <a href=\"https://root.cern.ch/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">ROOT</a>. Optimized the C++ software in the Linux environment and increased the signal significance by 200%.</p>"}}]}}}